speechtext:
Mr. Speaker, I rise in my place to present a petition that was sent to me by my constituents following the latest householder I put out in my riding. This petition states:
Whereas a clean and healthy environment is fundamental to our economic and social well-being and;
Whereas, past neglect of our environment has had a negative impact on many communities, one of which is the pollution of our rivers and streams and;
Whereas, the Rideau River in my riding of Ottawa- Vanier that has become polluted through many years of neglect, the undersigned petitioners humbly pray and call upon Parliament to ask the federal government to enter into an equal partnership with provincial and municipal governments to develop a plan of action for the clean-up and maintenance of the Rideau River.
